            <title>About</title>
            <link>http://localhost:4002/about/</link>
            <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:4002/about/</guid>
            <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hey-im-robin-&#34;&gt;Hey, I&amp;rsquo;m Robin 👋&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Builder, photographer, and lifelong tinkerer. ENTJ.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Live fully. Stay true.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I build things at the intersection of cloud and AI.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Currently a Senior Solutions Engineer at Microsoft. Previously at AWS serving ISV and SMB clients as Solutions Architect, and before that at IBM as Technical Solutions Architect. I design cloud-native architectures, ship AI-powered products, and help organizations make the most of their cloud investment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I care about clean architecture, developer experience, and making complex technology accessible. When I&amp;rsquo;m not architecting systems, I write about what I learn, build &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/robinsujob&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;open source tools&lt;/a&gt;, and capture the world through my &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/robinsu77/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;camera&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;explore&#34;&gt;Explore&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;📝 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:4002/post/&#34; &gt;Tech&lt;/a&gt; — Architecture patterns, AI/ML deep dives, and lessons from the field.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🛠 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:4002/projects/&#34; &gt;Projects&lt;/a&gt; — Open source tools and solutions I&amp;rsquo;ve built.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;📷 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/robinsu77/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Photography&lt;/a&gt; — Street, travel, architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;connect&#34;&gt;Connect&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/robinsujob&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/in/robin-su/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/robinsu77/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;</description>
