            <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;aws-solutions&#34;&gt;AWS Solutions&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2&#34;&gt;China CloudFront SSL Plugin V2&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;One-stop free SSL certificate management for China region CloudFront. V2 brings multi-project management, GUI interface, and Access Key authentication.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🔗 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/sample-China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin-V2&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/&#34; &gt;Blog Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tags:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS, CloudFront, SSL, Serverless&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin&#34;&gt;China CloudFront SSL Plugin&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Free SSL certificate deployment plugin for China region CloudFront (V1). Solves the lack of free SSL certificate provisioning and auto-renewal.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🔗 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/cloudfront-ssl-plugin-deployment-guide/&#34; &gt;Blog Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tags:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS, CloudFront, SSL&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;deploy-gguf-model-to-sagemaker&#34;&gt;Deploy GGUF Model to SageMaker&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Deploy quantized GGUF models on SageMaker using llama.cpp for efficient LLM inference.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🔗 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/deploy-gguf-model-to-sagemaker&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/sagemaker-gguf-model-inference/&#34; &gt;Blog Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tags:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS, SageMaker, LLM, GGUF&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;</description>
